Tron-inspired pinball game developed in Unreal Engine 5 using Blueprints.

# Features
- Flipper mechanics with impulse-based physics
- Ball launcher with charge-based power control
- Scoring system with multipliers and combo logic
- Bumpers, ramps, and trigger-based interactions
- UI scoreboard and game state flow
- Superbuy System

# Tech Stack
- Unreal Engine 5
- Blueprints
- Physics Constraints
- UMG (UI)


## Featured System - Super Buy Bonus Mode 
The Super buy System transitions the game into a Plinko-Style bonus mode featuring automated ball drops, multiplier bins, UI state updates and camera control.


# Status
In development

